looks promising but leads nowhere after 41 Rb1. Black should
prefer 38 Bc3 Rb5 with an edge.} Qd7 39.Be1 Nd5 {After 39
... Nd4 White's only move is 40 Ra1 but this is fine.} 40.Bd3
